advisory.title: `openpgp-card-sequoia` is unmaintained.
advisory.description: The [openpgp-card-sequoia](https://crates.io/crates/openpgp-card-sequoia) crate is no longer actively maintained. You can use the [openpgp-card-rpgp](https://crates.io/crates/openpgp-card-rpgp) crate for OpenPGP card client functionality instead.
